name: Age of Empires 2: DE Match Data
description:
The dataset contains roughly 225.000 matches played in Age of Empires 2: Definitive Edition in different granularity and connected Master Data.
The current version contains 3 levels:
-Match Level: featuring Match Id, Map, Map Size, Duration, Mean Elo, Civilizations, Starting Positions and Outcomes with one row per game
-Time Slice Level: contains the aggregated commands of type "Queue","Build" and "Research" made until a certain time in the game, with one row per game and one file per time slice. The games are sliced in 120 second slices. 
-Input Level: contains data about all made decisions in a game, with one row per input and one file per game.  

The information were collected by scraping and parsing AoE2:DE matches, using https://github.com/happyleavesaoc/aoc-mgz. The code for the underlying work can be found in https://github.com/nicoelbert/rtsgamestates.

Stay posted, for any questions feel free to get in touch.
